OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777903638
OL,3,CHMS Victory masts successfully removed
OL,4,Cin #42 million restoration project
OL,6,FThe removal of the masts from Vice-
OL,7,FAdmiral Lord Nelson's flagship HMS
OL,8,FVictory has been hailed as a "great
OL,9,Fsuccess" in the latest step to
OL,10,Fconserve the historic vessel.
OL,12,FA 750-tonne crane was used to remove
OL,13,FVictory's mizzen (rear), foremast
OL,14,F(front) and bowsprit (the bow).
OL,26,@pD@^OUqD@HO]
