PN,41402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777903638
OL,3,CHMS Victory masts successfully removed
OL,4,Cin #42 million restoration project
OL,6,FThe latest stage in the 10-year, #42
OL,7,Fmillion restoration project involved
OL,8,Fthe masts being removed and then
OL,9,Fsafely lowered and laid near the
OL,10,Fship's side at Portsmouth Historic
OL,11,FDockyard, ready for careful
OL,12,Fconservation work to begin.
OL,14,FThe front mast from the 18th century
OL,15,Fwarship was removed on Monday and
OL,16,Fanother two days of detailed work was
OL,17,Fneeded to move the mizzen and bowsprit.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777903638
OL,3,CHMS Victory masts successfully removed
OL,4,Cin #42 million restoration project
OL,6,FOn Saturday Patrizia Pierazzo, HMS
OL,7,FVictory deputy project director, said:
OL,8,F"The removal of the mizzen mast and
OL,9,Fbowsprit was a great success and
OL,10,Flessons learnt from the foremast
OL,11,Fremoval earlier in the week really
OL,12,Fhelped the team.
OL,14,F"This was a precise operation that
OL,15,Frequired input from a wide range of
OL,16,Fspecialists, and we're very pleased
OL,17,Fwith the outcome."
OL,19,FThe main mast was removed in 2021.
OL,26,@pD@AOUvD@AOUyD@RO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
