PN,41405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777903638
OL,3,CHMS Victory masts successfully removed
OL,4,Cin #42 million restoration project
OL,6,FAndrew Baines, executive director of
OL,7,Fmuseum operations for the National
OL,8,FMuseum of the Royal Navy (NMRN),
OL,9,Fpreviously described it as "a key
OL,10,Fmoment for The Big Repair project,
OL,11,Fbeing the first time Victory will have
OL,12,Fbeen without all her masts since the
OL,13,Fearly 1890s".
OL,15,FHe said: "Our team has planned this
OL,16,Fstep in meticulous detail but we still
OL,17,Fhave to work around factors like the
OL,18,Fweather.
OL,26,@qD@\OUuD@LO]wD@JOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
