PN,41406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777903638
OL,3,CHMS Victory masts successfully removed
OL,4,Cin #42 million restoration project
OL,6,F"That's why we will carry out the
OL,7,Flifts overnight, so we can work safely
OL,8,Fand without interruption for several
OL,9,Fhours at a time."
OL,11,FMr Baines added that once all the
OL,12,Fmasts were removed and safely stored
OL,13,F"we can begin the critical work of
OL,14,Fconserving them before their eventual
OL,15,Freturn to the ship in 2033".
OL,17,FStuart Sheldon, NMRN lead rigger,
OL,18,Fdescribed the lift as "complex" and
OL,19,Fneeding "absolute precision".
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@QO]uD@AOUwD@[O]zD@WOUzD@_O]{D@
